{"tid":2053271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【燒錯屍】大殮儀式後脫喪服離場 錯領遺體成黃家心結","createTime":"2020-06-06T06:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T13:29:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9174b68a501c6ec88e32d092cff5313e916e4dbc","tid":2053271,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"日前東華三院轄下位於紅磡的寰宇殯儀館，遭揭發錯將兩具先人遺體調亂，事件震驚殯儀界。終年79歲的姓黃老翁原定安排土葬，惟最終竟遭他人領取後火葬。黃家昨日在大角嘴九龍殯儀館為先人設靈，今日早上9時半開始進行大殮儀式，但由於黃翁遺體遭人錯領火化，故今日未能舉行出殯儀式。家人進行儀式時心情顯得加倍沉重，早上10時許儀式完結後，眾人脫下喪服後離場，事件始終成為黃家心結。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/breaking/20200606/TZFHEQEH2OCZM7HZ6LFXFMFASA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200606%2FTZFHEQEH2OCZM7HZ6LFXFMFASA%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=8c6e73b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200606%2FTZFHEQEH2OCZM7HZ6LFXFMFASA%2F&h=46cdf29e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/breaking/20200606/TZFHEQEH2OCZM7HZ6LFXFMFASA/</a>"},{"pid":"0591fb46ace9a8530faa41b6c504b7129ab8c144","tid":2053271,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"東華又係痴撚線"},{"pid":"f628f0547d803edb7e1153f441da3ad4aa66e503","tid":2053271,"uid":99700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"她又直指事件中錯領遺體的另一家人，曾將逝者安排在一個玻璃棺木內，並在5月18日某個大禮堂舉行了一次兩個半小時儀式，其間曾有超過150名親友瞻仰遺容，惟眾人竟沒有發現遺體有錯，令她感到十分疑惑。<br />\n屌？"},{"pid":"7efdb580ccc9da5442618e73cbf8cdd27ba4a830","tid":2053271,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"[so<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"